DataCamp Exercise

Sign-up

  • You must sign up using your @wayne.edu email.
  • Either sign up using the invite sent to your WSU email, or
  • Use the the link below
  • Click https://www.datacamp.com/groups/shared_links/3ef2335c9a202f1b126dbe09fc67734967a957ef64fe4ab69209d00039956246 to create your DataCamp account.

Check your progress

When you log in, you will see My Progress on the left. This is where you can track the assignments and their due dates.

Extra credit assignment

  • Go to https://www.datacamp.com and log in. You must use the ID/PW created from the above link or invite.
  • My_Progress and click Introduction to Oracle SQL
  • You must complete the entire course to get the extra credits
  • Your progress will be auto-saved on system. You dont need to submit anything on Canvas.
